---

Korálovka, an online discussion forum, held a meeting on October 27, 2023, focusing on the deteriorating quality of metal jewelry during the current economic crisis.

name: jewelry-fraud-rises-amid-cost-cutting
title: Jewelry Fraud Rises Amid Cost-Cutting
content: As people are cutting costs, there's an increase in fraudulent and harmful jewelry on the market. Customers have been reporting problems and scams encountered both in the Czech Republic and abroad.

name: jewelry-buying-guide-key-considerations
title: Jewelry Buying Guide: Key Considerations
content: Korálky Katlas has prepared a summary of important points to consider when purchasing finished jewelry and jewelry components, in response to these issues.
